high_descs: Walk forward and right to the kitchen sink
Pick up the knife from the sink
Cut the tomato in the sink with the knife
Put the knife down in the sink
Pick up a tomato slice from the sink
Turn left and walk forward to the microwave
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave then remove it
Turn left and walk over to the fridge
Open the fridge and put the tomato slice in it
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked tomato slice in the fridge

high_descs: Walk forward five steps, take a right for five steps, take a left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink, lying over the drain.
Cut off the stem of the tomato.
Slice up the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn left and walk to the microwave.

Open the microwave door and place the tomato on the far left part of the black plate then shut the door, turn on the microwave for a few seconds, open the door and take out the tomato slice and shut the door.
Turn left for one step, turn right and take one step, turn right and take another step and stand in front of the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door and place the tomato, vertically on the top shelf to the right of the silver pot and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of tomato into the refrigerator.

high_descs: move forward to the sink
pick up a knife from the sink
slice the tomato in the sink
drop the knife in the sink
pick up a slice of tomato
move left to the oven
place the tomato in the oven to cook and then take it out
turn  around and head to the fridge
place the tomato in the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a cooked tomato in the fridge
